name: Korporatio
product_desc:
Korporatio introduces the world’s first Legal Distributed Autonomous Organisation. Unlike other DAOs available on the blockchain today, a company set up with Korporatio is a compliant, trading entity. It has real world value.

The L-DAO can own assets, capital and employ people. The real world entity and the blockchain entity are not mirrors or copies. They are the same entity. If you trade shares in your company on the blockchain, that is part of your real world company you have sold. The changes you make to your company through the blockchain do not require any further endorsement, replication or action by a company secretary or other officer. The creation of your company incites the creation of a unique Ethereum side-chain token (ERC-20) just for your company. These are the company shares in real, practical and verifiable form.
markets: Cryptocurrency, Blockchains, Bitcoin Exchange, Blockchain / Cryptocurrency

name: Leverj
product_desc:
Leverj decentralizes the most desirable features of derivatives trading by implementing them in cryptocurrencies and eliminating points of friction.  With a tight focus on derivatives trading and the supporting ecosystem, Leverj has taken the approach of defining the product first.  We have built a functioning exchange with a usable UI (user interface), decentralized identity, and provable audit.  We plan to decentralize the back-end and add ecosystem features that will enable large players to move into the cryptocurrency world.

Leverj operates on the Ethereum Blockchain as a base platform.  Decentralized custody and assurance of cryptographically secure funds require smart contracts in our high-speed, trustless protocol.  In the current state of the Bitcoin network, the decentralized model has become prohibitively expensive.  Ethereum transactions are faster and cheaper, making it the natural step forward for further developing a decentralized trading platform.
markets: Financial Exchanges, Finance Technology, Cryptocurrency, Bitcoin Exchange

name: Solion International
product_desc:
XDRAW allows large (unlimited) player numbers to compete against each other on the same table and at the same time for correspondingly large pots.  This gives the game a major Viral Potential in that large player numbers create large pots, which in turn attract more players...

XDRAW is the World's biggest and fastest Poker Game!

Keep in mind that what we mean by "large player numbers" for XDRAW differs in form and substance from all other forms of Poker.  The XDRAW table provides simultaneous concurrent competitive play between an unlimited number of players.  All other Poker formats are sequential with small player numbers.  While other Poker Formats may have "large player numbers", players are distributed over a correspondingly  large number of Poker Tables, they do not build a single Pot, they do not have a sense of competing against "large player numbers" and players must wait sequentially for every other player.

XDRAW - a new unlimited & timed competitive internet poker format.
high_concept: Launching XDRAW - the World's biggest and fastest Poker Game!
